  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Authorizes the New York power authority to supply electric energy to low-income households receiving assistance through the New York city human resources administration and the New York state office of temporary and disability assistance, and to designate such agencies and local social services districts as billing energy service companies."
    }
